      "text": "The goroutine is unparked\nonly when something arrives\nin the accept queue.",
      "fontSize": 60.53514223443345,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The goroutine is unparked only when something arrives in the accept queue.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "gRwsrH5pf9qeCDEIkwJfM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.6769350616669,
      "y": 3697.6694931111215,
      "width": 281.11981201171875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Owkr5wB9S-0KHa0CBviXe"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJn",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1313950779,
      "version": 84,
      "versionNonce": 1130102773,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777746208990,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What actually happens in Go:",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "What actually happens in Go:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "cBJuxnEHGwkQxJSWKiJOb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.8054160845604,
      "y": 3755.1694931111215,
      "width": 718.8195190429688,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Owkr5wB9S-0KHa0CBviXe"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJo",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 275909851,
      "version": 85,
      "versionNonce": 2242901,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777746208990,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Accept() is called — the goroutine asks the Go runtime \"give me the next\nconnection from the accept queue\"",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Accept() is called — the goroutine asks the Go runtime \"give me the next connection from the accept queue\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "dx1Ar24hndBwBgfPoRrSY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.8054160845604,
      "y": 3821.1454260386727,
      "width": 761.4194946289062,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Owkr5wB9S-0KHa0CBviXe"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 502380923,
      "version": 87,
      "versionNonce": 781862581,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777746208990,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "If the accept queue is empty, the Go runtime parks the goroutine (removes it\nfrom the OS thread, marks it as waiting)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If the accept queue is empty, the Go runtime parks the goroutine (removes it from the OS thread, marks it as waiting)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "_Vx5JQ7VqGHFGG03QIso4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.8054160845604,
      "y": 3887.1213589662257,
      "width": 713.9395141601562,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Owkr5wB9S-0KHa0CBviXe"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 68342299,
      "version": 89,
      "versionNonce": 1634314261,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777746208990,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The kernel handles the entire handshake independently — no goroutine is\ninvolved, no thread is consumed",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The kernel handles the entire handshake independently — no goroutine is involved, no thread is consumed",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KwazcCI8lasUB05Hj4-kl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.8054160845604,
      "y": 3953.0972918937787,
      "width": 768.719482421875,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Owkr5wB9S-0KHa0CBviXe"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 63428283,
      "version": 145,
      "versionNonce": 981851509,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777746208991,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When the ACK arrives and the kernel moves cli:tcp_sock to ESTABLISHED and\nputs it in the accept queue, the kernel fires an epoll event on the listening\nsocket's fd",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When the ACK arrives and the kernel moves cli:tcp_sock to ESTABLISHED and puts it in the accept queue, the kernel fires an epoll event on the listening socket's fd",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "No_i0df8HgHE8ncAk1nWx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.8054160845604,
      "y": 4044.07322482133,
      "width": 760.5393676757812,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Owkr5wB9S-0KHa0CBviXe"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJs",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 464734043,
      "version": 124,
      "versionNonce": 20211413,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777746208991,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Go's netpoller (running on a separate OS thread) picks up this epoll event and\nunparks the goroutine",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Go's netpoller (running on a separate OS thread) picks up this epoll event and unparks the goroutine",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BarFRxgJMk46gCIP_320I",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.8054160845604,
      "y": 4110.049157748883,
      "width": 526.2596435546875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Owkr5wB9S-0KHa0CBviXe"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1378329595,
      "version": 122,
      "versionNonce": 2013971509,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777746208991,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The goroutine resumes, Accept() returns conn (fd=10)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The goroutine resumes, Accept() returns conn (fd=10)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZbDLYDGi9qNvRf8qFstTY",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -5633.57961232386,
      "y": 3337.9361814399817,
      "width": 278.0422736743133,
      "height": 75.83508281007045,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJu",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1059548315,
      "version": 152,
      "versionNonce": 1928230293,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "MVYk43Zl-u4MMqgiOmnkv"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1777746208991,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "MVYk43Zl-u4MMqgiOmnkv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -5616.33839034266,
      "y": 3363.353722845017,
      "width": 243.55982971191406,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bJv",
